column2: "This match might have been arranged pretty hastily, but don't expect us to hold anything back!"
"When Kirito and I are by each other's sides, there's nothing we can't overcome."
"I've heard that you two are the strongest in this world when you're together."
"If that's true, I want to see you at your best. I don't want any regrets when we have to leave this world..."
"The arena will be Harkotan's Successive Training! Let's go, Guardians!"
